channel.title: Port Clogged, or closed?!?!
channel.description: Ok guys, My server worked fine for about 3 months, Then no one could log on anymore, The PF Checker, said my port was closed, so i re-PFED, and it still said closed....So i bought the PFConfig, And It PFED for me, but it still was closed! I Dont know what im going to do! Im on a Wireless router...."Actiontec - GT724-WG" SOME ONE HELP ME RE-OPEN MY PORT! 43594!

item.title: Port Clogged, or closed?!?!
item.dc:creator: @MoparScaperDude MoparScaperDude
item.description:
@MoparScaperDude wrote:

Just to tell you - your ports will only appear open if you’re running the server. If you’re not running it, but they’re forwarded, they will not appear open, because they’re not open for connections since the server wouldn’t be running.
